---

<section id="hero" class="hero">
    <div class="hero-container">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <p class="hero-kicker">Cuidado diario para tu piel</p>
            <h1>Skincare sencillo y lleno de cariño</h1>
            <p class="hero-text">Productos inspirados en el cuidado coreano con asesoramiento cercano. Calidad que se siente y se ve.</p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
                <a href="/productos" class="btn btn-primary">Explorar productos</a>
                <a href="/blogexp" class="btn btn-secondary">Consejos de expertos</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-card">
            <p class="hero-card-title">Rutina recomendada</p>
            <p class="hero-card-text">Limpia, hidrata y protege en 3 pasos con formulas suaves para uso diario.</p>
            <a href="/productos" class="hero-card-link">Ver rutina ></a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
<style>
    .hero {
        min-height: 100vh;
        width: 100%;
        position: relative;
        background: linear-gradient(
                135deg,
                #fff8efde,
                #fff8ef8f
            ),
            url("../assets/banner.webp");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        width: 100%;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 130px 36px 80px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
        gap: 36px;
        align-items: end;
    }

    .hero-content {
        max-width: 640px;
    }

    .hero-kicker {
        font-size: 14px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif;
        color: #7a5e49;
        margin: 0 0 12px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
        font-size: 62px;
        color: #000000;
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        font-family: Playfair Display, serif;
        line-height: 1.03;
    }

    .hero-text {
        font-size: 21px;
        color: #2f2f2f;
        line-height: 1.55;
        font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        max-width: 560px;
    }

    .hero-actions {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 14px;
        margin-top: 30px;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 22px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 15px;
        font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 700;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .btn-primary {
        background-color: #ff6f91;
        color: #fff;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
        background-color: #ef5b80;
    }

    .btn-secondary {
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
        color: #2f2f2f;
        border: 1px solid rgba(84, 60, 43, 0.22);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
        background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
    }

    .hero-card {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        border: 1px solid rgba(84, 60, 43, 0.22);
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 22px;
        max-width: 370px;
        justify-self: end;
    }

    .hero-card-title {
        margin: 0;
        color: #2a2a2a;
        font-family: Playfair Display, serif;
        font-size: 30px;
        line-height: 1.1;
    }

    .hero-card-text {
        margin: 12px 0 0;
        color: #3a3a3a;
        font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .hero-card-link {
        margin-top: 14px;
        display: inline-block;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #b84d6c;
        font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 14px;
        letter-spacing: 0.03em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
        .hero {
            min-height: auto;
        }

        .hero-container {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: 22px;
            padding: 120px 20px 60px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 48px;
        }

        .hero-text {
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .hero-card {
            justify-self: start;
            max-width: 460px;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 620px) {
        .hero-container {
            padding: 120px 16px 42px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 38px;
        }

        .hero-kicker {
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .btn {
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero-card-title {
            font-size: 25px;
        }

    }
</style>
